\[\frac{d^2 }{d\tau^2} (x^\mu + \xi^\mu) + \Gamma^\mu_{\ \ \alpha \beta} (x+\xi) \frac{d}{d\tau} (x^\alpha + \xi^\alpha) \frac{d}{d\tau} (x^\beta + \xi^\beta)
= F^\mu_\mathrm{ext} (x+\xi) \tag{2}\]

